same area as well. And I was wondering if you could just describe that a little bit more about

00:05:30.519 --> 00:05:38.519
what that means, operational risk. Yeah, so as a company, the business continuity team

00:05:39.079 --> 00:05:46.359
is responsible for being able to re-establish all our business processes in case of a

00:05:46.359 --> 00:05:51.880
catastrophe, like Hurricane Sandy or something like that, people can't get into the office.

