a matrix organization. There's a lot of people that have dual reporting relationships up and

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:55.239
so I'm now part of operational risk management, which is a fairly small group, because the

00:10:56.359 --> 00:11:03.320
thinking is that the actual owner of the risk is the owner of the business process. And so

00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:11.080
they're in the business and they have resources that are knowledgeable about risk management as

